author: Screen Junkies
description:
You're in for a treat with tomorrow's Honest Trailer as we dive into the latest film classic, War of the Worlds, starring Ice Cube. A movie so bad, you'll wish the alien invasion was real and relieve you of having to watch the whole thing. Thanks Amazon for the content to keep us busy!

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)
Title Design: Robert Holtby
title: Honest Trailers Preview - War of the Worlds (2025)
